- Tech stack: React (vite), Tailwind, ShadCN, Firebase Auth, Supabase postgres, pnpm, Node.JS, Hono API, trpc, drizzle
- Use `pnpm add` when installing new packages.
- Use `npx shadcn@latest add` to add new shadcn components.
- You are not able to see or modify .env files directly - so tell the user what they should add to the file if needed.
- Never commit files from the ./docs/features folder